title: Ek Aur Mrityu Pujan
subTitle: When the shadow of evil starts taking over the world, a warrior fights for good, as an avatar of Narasimha, a lion god, who is known for destroying evil.

title: Yuvaraj
subTitle: Yuva enrols in an engineering college after getting banned from his sport and picks up fights with local students. However, his life gets more strained when his father flees, owing a huge debt.

title: Bhoot
subTitle: Swati and Vishal move into a new flat that is haunted by the spirit of its previous tenant. Later, Vishal observes a sudden shift in Swati's behaviour.

title: Colors Cineplex HD
subTitle: Bringing the best in television.

title: Karkash
subTitle: A wayward husband vows to punish his dutiful wife after a false rumour spreads in society that questions her fidelity. Eventually, the woman must take dire measures to prove her loyalty and honour.

title: Angrezi Mein Kehte Hain
subTitle: Yashwant, a middle-aged man, refrains from expressing his love for his wife, Kiran. As a result, their relationship develops cracks and they decide to part ways.

title: Ek Zakhmi Romeo
subTitle: Ananya loves her best friend, Surya, while he falls for another woman, Pooja. However, after his heartbreak, Surya is too late to realise who truly loved him as Ananya rejects him.

title: Deewar Man of Power
subTitle: Childhood friends Bujji and Chitti decide to meet after 12 years. Bujji, a gangster, attempts to murder Sivanna, not knowing that he is Chitti's brother.

title: Spy
subTitle: An agent investigates the death of his elder brother with the help of his fellow agents. However, his actions lead to the discovery of a nuclear plot against India.

title: Etharkkum Thunindhavan
subTitle: Kannabiran, a lawyer, saves a young woman from a pornography racket run by Inba, a minister's son. However, Inba threatens to leak explicit videos of several women, making Kannabiran go after him.

title: Mardaani 2
subTitle: A twenty-one-year-old psychopath has an affinity towards raping and murdering young woman. But, a cop, Shivani Shivaji Roy, is on his heels as she tries to bring him to justice.

title: Gatta Kusthi
subTitle: Veera has a preconceived set of criteria for what he wants in a bride. However, he ends up unexpectedly marrying a woman who is the complete opposite of his expectations.

title: Alluri
subTitle: Iqbal, an aspiring police candidate, embarks on a journey to follow in the footsteps of Alluri, an upright officer, and discovers valuable lessons along the way.

title: Mission 118
subTitle: An investigative journalist has nightmares about a young woman's murder and tries to uncover whether his dreams have any connection to reality.

title: Mission 118
subTitle: An investigative journalist has nightmares about a young woman's murder and tries to uncover whether his dreams have any connection to reality.

title: Time Machine
subTitle: Friends Elango and Pulivetti stumble upon a time machine and exploit it for personal gain. Things take a turn when they alter a gangster's fate, leading to unforeseen and dangerous consequences.

title: Indra Shakti
subTitle: A young couple is all set to get married, but an evil businessman and his henchmen brutally murder them. The lovers then return as ghosts to exact revenge on their perpetrators.

title: City of Gold
subTitle: Jonathan Davenport journeys to the Amazon rainforest with his estranged lover to seek out a reclusive artist. However, the mission soon brings out something dark and dangerous within himself.

title: Rowdy Baadshah
subTitle: A man fails to get a job with the police force due to his father's connections with a gangster. However, when his brother is killed by the latter, he sets out on the path of revenge.

title: Aavesham
subTitle: Three boys move into a hostel to pursue engineering, where they clash with seniors. To get revenge, they befriend a gangster.

title: Maragadha Naanayam
subTitle: Senguttuvan and Elango work for a smuggler who hires them to retrieve an emerald medallion, a cursed treasure linked to many deaths. Seeking help, they consult a priest and summon three spirits to locate it.

title: The Family Star
subTitle: Govardhan, a diligent architect, longs for a partner who understands his commitment to his large family. When Indu, a new tenant, moves in, his life starts to unfold in a new direction.

title: Dil Hai Tumhaara
subTitle: Sarita raises Shalu, her spouse's love child, and her daughter, Nimmi, but she does not forgive Shalu's past. When she discovers that Shalu is growing close to Nimmi's lover, things become worse.

title: Maargan
subTitle: A serial killer targets women with a strange serum that turns their bodies black. Subsequently, a high-ranking police officer sets out to catch the culprit.

title: Liger -- Saala Crossbreed
subTitle: A talented young MMA fighter trains hard to rise up the ranks. However, his goals are hindered when his lover is kidnapped.

title: Liger -- Saala Crossbreed
subTitle: A talented young MMA fighter trains hard to rise up the ranks. However, his goals are hindered when his lover is kidnapped.

title: International Khiladi: The Iron Man
subTitle: Amrita's parents get killed. Years later, she falls in love with Aditya only to learn that he was the one who was accused of her parents' murder.

title: Uvaa
subTitle: Five teenagers, who lead a carefree life, face challenges at their new convent school. Although their intentions are purely romantic, a horrifying event threatens to change their lives forever.

title: Lekar Hum Deewana Dil
subTitle: Dino and Karishma get married in Goa and head to the lesser-known parts of the country, afraid of being caught by their parents. However, they start facing multiple challenges in their marital life.

title: Mickey Virus
subTitle: When the woman he loves regrets a web transaction, a hacker decides to help her undo it. However, chaos ensues when he accidentally commits a robbery instead.

title: Ruslaan
subTitle: Ruslaan, a terrorist's son, undergoes a major life change when an anti-terrorism officer adopts him. Determined to fix his bad reputation, Ruslaan becomes an intelligence agent.

title: Chithha
subTitle: Living a quiet life with his niece, Eeswaran manages to provide for her and nurtures her like a parent. However, his journey takes an insidous turn when she goes missing.

title: Buddy
subTitle: A terrible accident leaves Pallavi in a coma while her soul possesses the body of a teddy bear. With her organs in danger of being traded, she enlists the help of a pilot, Aditya.

title: MCA: Middle Class Abbayi
subTitle: Nani, a middle-class boy with an eidetic memory, helps save his sister-in-law from a goon. Meanwhile, he also tries to convince his girlfriend's father to marry her off to him.

title: Saindhav
subTitle: A man with a traumatic past is compelled to encounter an crime boss so that he can rescue his daughter from a health problem.

title: Surya's Saturday
subTitle: Surya, a young man with anger issues, channels his emotions on Saturdays, because of a promise to his deceased mother. However, things get complicated when he decides to confront a corrupt cop.

title: Taqdeerwala
subTitle: Yamraj and Chitragupt descend to Earth to look for the missing book of destiny. Soon, they find it in the possession of a man who refuses to part with it because it contains information of his mother's lifespan.
